# Web Frontend Rule

- Keep browser-only code in `apps/web`; do not import server-only modules.
- Use accessible-first UI patterns and test user-visible behavior.
- Prefer `Vitest` + Testing Library queries by role/name over brittle selectors.
- When changing UI behavior, update/add tests in `apps/web/src/**/*.test.tsx?`.
- Keep shared contracts/types in `packages/shared` instead of duplicating.
- Run `npm run ci:test:full` before finalizing cross-workspace changes.
